    O - The type of the output of a net front neuron.

    public final class FrontNetNeuron<O>
extends Neuronoid<FrontNetNeuron<O>,java.lang.Object,O>

    A net front neuron is a neuron that connects to a net back neuron. A net front neuron is closable.

    Silvan Wyss
